Install apache2 + database program
Install Django
Install Git
Pull code from Github
Install libapache-mod-wsgi

Make sure you have the isoweek python installed using:
"sudo pip install isoweek"

edit /etc/apache2/httpd.conf (if non existent, create one and add "Include httpd.conf" to the end of the apache2.conf file) and follow the instructions https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/1.4/howto/deployment/wsgi/modwsgi/


Initialize database with name and user
Configure Studiereis/settings.py. provide correct user, installed apps, template directory (USE ABSOLUTE PATHS!!!) etc
Configure Studiereis/urls.py (add app)
chown -R www-data:www-data Studiereis/* in de map waar de website staat
